{"tid":1910510,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"USB裝WIN10問題","createTime":"2020-03-04T17:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T11:38:26.000Z","uid":44935,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f967cc606f1d27229ea5eca427b7c9b3028bae5f","tid":1910510,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩買左部新電腦，整左個usb諗住裝win10落去<br />\n去左bios set好左boot option #1係隻usb，save完 exit之後，部腦去到呢個畫面就死左係度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OecEn6S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOecEn6S.jpg&h=e030ec79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個圓圈轉都兩個圈就停左係度<br />\n<br />\n然後我用同一隻手指插落部舊機都，佢又可以load到入去洗腦個畫面度<br />\n<br />\n請問咁多位巴打知唔知發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果開錯台，有怪莫怪，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadce7aee25a9c577ebf0b26f7de33e413cc96f9","tid":1910510,"uid":40369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"插機後面usb 2.0頭試試"},{"pid":"db49ff25a5c1e21eeb25ab7c20425a71588852e1","tid":1910510,"uid":44935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cadce7aee25a9c577ebf0b26f7de33e413cc96f9","tid":1910510,"uid":40369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"插機後面usb 2.0頭試試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩試左了，佢都係唔係"},{"pid":"73255abd28ac250fffcc38d054e0788f495d5643","tid":1910510,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"搵另一個iso裝過啦"},{"pid":"bb3d847945484d93cfc8aa1eff73c82da60f7aba","tid":1910510,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"